<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4337.4.9>
    dc:creator "Vörös, Judit; Dias, Iuri Ribeiro; Solé, Mirco" ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Phyllodytes (Anura: Hylidae) from the Atlantic Rainforest of southern Bahia, Brazil" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1034334>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1034336>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1034338>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1034340> .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1034334>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Phyllodytes amadoi SP. nov. in preservative (holotype, MZUESC 14954, SVL = 20 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1034334/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1034336>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Phyllodytes amadoi SP. nov., holotype MZUESC 14954, ventral views of hand (A) and foot (B); dorsal (C) and lateral (D) view of the head. Drawing courtesy of Viktória Szőke (HNHM)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1034336/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1034338>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Photos of Phyllodytes amadoi SP. nov., paratype MZUESC 14995 in life. Photos: Mirco Solé." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1034338/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1034340>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. (A) Oscillogram and corresponding spectrogram of the advertisement call of Phyllodytes amadoi SP. nov. (holotype). Detailed example of firsts notes of the call being shorter (B) and final notes longer and with initial pulses interspaced from the rest of the note (C). Recorded on 7 th of October 2015 at 19 h 30 min. Air temperature during recording = 22.6 ° C." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1034340/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

